data.description: Rare find in East Valley*Beautiful Gilbert Golf Course home with Pool*Premium Lot*Haven''t seen ANY GOLF BALLS in the yard*Upgraded with 3 Bay Windows Views of the Golf Course and Pool from most areas in home.
